      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "title": "Hero skills",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "A skill is a one-of-a-kind action performed by and available in-game only to a specific hero."
          },
          {
            "text": "Each of these special moves contributes to a hero's skill set."
          },
          {
            "text": "Almost all heroes will have an innate ability, two normal abilities, and one ultimate ability."
          },
          {
            "text": "In some rare cases, a hero may have three normal abilities and one ultimate ability."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "templates": [
