  {
    "title": "Obtaining a hero",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "To use a hero in a match, you must obtain them by purchasing directly by using, , or."
          },
          {
            "text": "A hero can also be obtained in certain events."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Every week, a random selection of five heroes is made available for use in all matches with the exception of the Ranked game mode, but this does not mean you obtained them.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Ranked"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Trial cards can also be used to try a hero for free for a limited time.",
            "links": [
              {
                "text": "Trial cards",
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Trial card"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "Once activated, the hero can now be used to participate in matches (except Ranked) until the free trial period ends."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
